            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app><note>Text from autopsy</note></app>
                    <app loc="1"><note>Traces of the feet of three letters, one of them curved, but not readily identifiable</note></app>
                    <app loc="2"><note>The vertical at the start of the line is readily compatible with a T; there is a vertical preserved on the break at the end of the line.</note></app>
                </listApp>
